      "id": "PopularPost174869",
      "post_content": "@tavaritz: It was so you could (for whatever reason) effectively put 8 [Drudge Skeletons](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Drudge Skeletons) in a deck at once. They did something similar with [Walking Dead](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Walking Dead) in Legends, although Walking Dead had the advantage of being a Zombie and not a Skeleton.  \n  \nStill, it's another Drudge. Good for singleton or EDH when you want more than one. Deserves the exact same rating as Drudge (right now around a 4), not this below 3 nonsense.",
      "posted_by": "yyukichigai",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost174869\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">@tavaritz: It was so you could (for whatever reason) effectively put 8 <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Drudge Skeletons\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Drudge Skeletons\">Drudge Skeletons</a> in a deck at once.  They did something similar with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Walking Dead\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Walking Dead\">Walking Dead</a> in Legends, although Walking Dead had the advantage of being a Zombie and not a Skeleton.<br/><br/>Still, it's another Drudge.  Good for singleton or EDH when you want more than one.  Deserves the exact same rating as Drudge (right now around a 4), not this below 3 nonsense.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '174869'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy65090\">yyukichigai</span>\r\n                                (7/5/2011 7:15:30 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_c