      "post_content": "I always wondered the decision on renaming creatures, but not non-creatures, when reprinting cards in new expansion. IMHO they all should have the same name.  \n  \nWhy do I need to check what are the characteristics of Restless Dead when I know those of [Drudge Skeletons](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Drudge Skeletons)?  \n  \nOr was there some reason that you needed eight of them in one deck?",
